snippet.title: Amber Guyger exchanged explicit texts with partner before deadly shooting
snippet.description:
We're learning new details about the night a former Dallas police officer shot and killed her neighbor in his home, as her murder trial continues. Amber Guyger claims she thought she was in her own apartment and Botham Jean was a burglar. Omar Villafranca reports.
